  "synopsis": "Five girls including Yui Tsukishima were summoned into the end of Edo period by the power of mystic stones jewel (known as Hojous'). They became the current Tennyo replacing the previous Tennyo who fell in battle. Through the use of their powers, and \"the Power of Word,\" they fight back the two demon brothers who sought to destroy humankind, using the powers they've gained.\n\nThis story is about a true to life Rakugo Storyteller (named Utamaru Katsura) who wants nothing more then to make Yui (a very happy cheerful girl) an capable professional in the \"art of Rakugoing.\"\n\nIn otherwords, a comedy, with a punchline told in a story.",
